ted our values of openness, community, excellence, and user data privacy. arXiv is committed to these values and only works with partners that adhere to them.\n\nHave an idea for a project that will add value for arXiv's community? [**Learn more about arXivLabs**](https://info.arxiv.org/labs/index.html).\n\n[Which authors of this paper are endorsers?](/auth/show-endorsers/2311.12732) | [Disable MathJax](javascript:setMathjaxCookie\\(\\)) ([What is MathJax?](https://info.arxiv.org/help/mathjax.html))\n\n-   [About](https://info.arxiv.org/about)\n-   [Help](https://info.arxiv.org/help)\n\n-   contact arXivClick here to contact arXiv [Contact](https://info.arxiv.org/help/contact.html)\n-   subscribe to arXiv mailingsClick here to subscribe [Subscribe](https://info.arxiv.org/help/subscribe)\n\n-   [Copyright](https://info.arxiv.org/help/license/index.html)\n-   [Privacy Policy](https://info.arxiv.org/help/policies/privacy_policy.html)\n\n-   [Web Accessibility Assistance](https://info.arxiv.org/help/web_accessibility.html)\n-   [arXiv Operational Status](https://status.arxiv.org)","metadata":{"truncated":false},"title":"https://arxiv.org/abs/2311.12732 (text/html; charset=utf-8)","time":{"start":1780128633096,"end":1780128633207}},"id":"prt_e77ef4eaf001J3zo6x1m5vg351","sessionID":"ses_1881128e0ffeiiErkDtN1kfFl9","messageID":"msg_e77ef2db40017yIV73FQyefzar"}}
