{"type":"text","timestamp":1780128821793,"sessionID":"ses_1881128e0ffeiiErkDtN1kfFl9","part":{"id":"prt_e77f22761001cP9TFD1KH71BVU","messageID":"msg_e77f21c160016Yp20jofARjSwZ","sessionID":"ses_1881128e0ffeiiErkDtN1kfFl9","type":"text","text":"Iteration 2 complete. Designed a 6-stage hint-free dispatch harness with three trace-capture approaches, a 5-category contamination taxonomy with pre-dispatch grep gate, and expected-resource-key hold-out using the skill's own RESOURCE_MAP as canonical truth — 8 findings captured across `iteration-002.md`, `iter-002.jsonl`, and `deltas/iter-002.jsonl`.","time":{"start":1780128819041,"end":1780128821792}}}
